{"entries":[{"id":"classic-olafur-eliasson","name":"Olafur Eliasson","category":"藝術家","tier":"經典檔案庫","region":"西方","country":"丹麥 / 冰島","media":["裝置","光/影像/投影","聲音/霧/水"],"works":"The Weather Project；The New York City Waterfalls；Ice Watch","comment":"把氣候、感知與公共壯觀結合；他的作品常在美學快感之後留下環境問題。","website":"https://olafureliasson.net/","workPage":"https://olafureliasson.net/artwork/the-new-york-city-waterfalls-2008/","photo":"https://olafureliasson.net/studio","classicTitle":"The New York City Waterfalls","classicImage":"https://res.cloudinary.com/olafureliasson-net/image/private/q_auto:eco,c_fit,h_640,w_640/img/the-new-york-city-waterfalls_4047.jpg","classicDesc":"The New York City Waterfalls 在紐約水岸建立四座人工瀑布，把都市基礎設施轉成短暫自然奇觀。它的重要性在於讓環境、工程與城市觀光同時成為作品語言。","status":"官方來源","updated":"2026-07-03"},{"id":"classic-anish-kapoor","name":"Anish Kapoor","category":"藝術家","tier":"經典檔案庫","region":"西方","country":"英國 / 印度","media":["雕塑","裝置","建築/場域"],"works":"Cloud Gate；Marsyas；Descension","comment":"以鏡面、空洞與深色體量改寫城市觀看經驗；作品常成為地標，但核心是空間心理學。","website":"https://anishkapoor.com/","workPage":"https://anishkapoor.com/","photo":"https://anishkapoor.com/","classicTitle":"Cloud Gate","classicImage":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Redirect/file/Cloud_Gate_%28The_Bean%29_from_east%27.jpg","classicDesc":"Cloud Gate 以無縫不鏽鋼鏡面扭曲芝加哥天際線與觀眾身體，成為城市自我凝視的裝置。它看似親民地標，實際上把公共雕塑、觀光、自拍文化與城市品牌壓縮在同一個反射面上。","status":"官方來源","updated":"2026-07-03"},{"id":"classic-michael-heizer","name":"Michael Heizer","category":"藝術家","tier":"經典檔案庫","region":"西方","country":"美國","media":["地景/大地藝術","雕塑","建築/場域"],"works":"Double Negative；City；Levitated Mass","comment":"他的尺度接近考古遺址與工程地貌；公共性不是人潮，而是文明尺度的時間想像。","website":"https://www.tripleaughtfoundation.org/","workPage":"https://www.tripleaughtfoundation.org/city","photo":"https://gagosian.com/artists/michael-heizer/","classicTitle":"City","classicImage":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/55/City_Art.PNG","classicDesc":"City 是 Heizer 在內華達沙漠耗時數十年完成的巨型土方與混凝土結構，尺度接近考古遺址。它把當代藝術、古文明想像與土地工程合併，幾乎拒絕一般展覽節奏。","status":"官方來源","updated":"2026-07-03"},{"id":"classic-robert-smithson","name":"Robert Smithson","category":"藝術家","tier":"經典檔案庫","region":"西方","country":"美國","media":["地景/大地藝術","裝置"],"works":"Spiral Jetty；Partially Buried Woodshed；Non-sites","comment":"他把地質、熵與藝術制度連在一起；Spiral Jetty 是大地藝術最核心的原型之一。","website":"https://holtsmithsonfoundation.org/robert-smithson","workPage":"https://holtsmithsonfoundation.org/spiral-jetty","photo":"https://holtsmithsonfoundation.org/robert-smithson","classicTitle":"Spiral Jetty","classicImage":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/84/Spiral-jetty-from-rozel-point.png","classicDesc":"Spiral Jetty 以岩石與土方在大鹽湖中形成螺旋，隨水位、鹽晶與時間變化。它是大地藝術的原型，不把自然當背景，而讓地質、熵與觀看條件共同完成作品。","status":"官方來源","updated":"2026-07-03"}]}